REST backend for the TodoList application
(no page rendering here, just sending json to client)


Purpose:
  REST backend

Install:
    $ npm install

	Need mocha, chai and requset for testing
    $ npm install -g mocha
    $ npm install chai
    $ npm install request


Compile:
  -

Test:
 - There are some mocha test, see test/...
 - Or use curl (manual or make a script)

Run:
  Move to dir with app.js file

  $ npm install nodemon -g
  $ nodemon     (not app.js after)

  Visit localhost:3000
